about.summary: A pure Python implementation of systemd's service notification protocol (sd_notify)

name: sdnotify
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sdnotify" %}
{% set version = "0.3.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 73977fc746b36cc41184dd43c3fe81323e7b8b06c2bb0826c4f59a20c56bb9f1

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - sdnotify

about:
  home: "https://github.com/bb4242/sdnotify"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: "A pure Python implementation of systemd's service notification protocol (sd_notify)"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
